data.description: Discover an extraordinary opportunity with 3 Cedar Lane in Shawnee, Oklahoma. This rustic home, nestled on a scenic 2-acre lot, invites you to unlock its hidden potential and transform it into a remarkable haven. While currently in need of renovation, envision the charm and serenity this property could exude with your personal touch. Majestic trees and expansive grounds provide the perfect backdrop for your creative aspirations. Embrace the chance to reimagine living in this tranquil setting, just moments from Shawnee's amenities. Unleash your imagination and seize the moment to own 3 Cedar Lane—a canvas for your dreams to flourish.
